title: The Best bits of the Late Show Vol. 3
creator_credit: D Generation, ABC-TV (Australia), Michael Hirsch, Mark Gibson and Joe Murray
brief_description: Finally all the ‘classic’ Logie-winning moments from the Logie-winning second series of the Logie-winning D-Generation’s Logie-winning ‘The Late Show’. See such cult classics as: Shitscared, Glengarry Glenn Ridge, Charlie the Wonderdog, Schwarzenegger’s Citizen Kane, The Oz Brothers, Mick’s underpants, Street interviews galore, spectacular, musical finals, including Joan Kirner doing Joan Jett, plus dozens more ‘Champagne Comedy’ sketches.
